about her father.

56:27.260 --> 56:28.921
Knows what?

56:29.595 --> 56:31.506
That he killed himself.

56:35.393 --> 56:37.054
She didn't know that?

56:38.813 --> 56:41.395
I told her it was an accident.

56:45.736 --> 56:47.601
Today I realized...

56:49.073 --> 56:51.234
(Sighs) ..she knows.

56:52.577 --> 56:54.818
Maybe she's always known.

56:54.954 --> 56:57.240
—Toni
-Mm?

56:59.625 --> 57:01.786
Kids...do stuff.

57:01.919 --> 57:03.375
I did stuff.

57:03.504 --> 57:05.460
Jeez.

57:05.590 --> 57:08.047
The shit I did... Do.

57:10.052 --> 57:12.338
She's a good kid.

57:12.471 --> 57:14.336
She's angry as hell.

57:15.391 --> 57:16.676
Yeah.

57:17.643 --> 57:19.224
She has every right to be.

57:21.731 --> 57:23.813
Angry at her father.

57:25.401 --> 57:26.891
Angry at me.

57:31.490 --> 57:33.526
- (Car door closes)
— (Don) You're late.

57:33.659 --> 57:35.775
(Cornell chuckles) And hungover too.

57:35.911 --> 57:38.698
Ash Wednesday — sounds about right.

57:38.831 --> 57:42.119
(Cornell) Yeah.
(Sonny) So you're going out too, huh?

57:42.251 --> 57:44.082
At least a couple of days a week.

57:44.211 --> 57:46.202
Every chance I get.

57:47.465 --> 57:49.296
Shit's got me clean.

57:49.425 --> 57:51.256
Keeps me clean too.

57:51.385 --> 57:52.921
Yeah, I get it.

57:53.054 --> 57:56.296
You're gonna talk some noble shit about
putting in a good hard day's work, huh?

57:56.432 --> 57:57.763
Hell, no.

57:57.892 --> 58:01.976
It's just there ain't no place out here
to party and get fucked up.

58:02.104 --> 58:04.971
- (Bell dings)
— You're right about that.

58:11.322 --> 58:13.563
How was your Mardi Gras?

58:13.699 --> 58:15.906
— (Laughing)
— (Engine starts)

58:22.708 --> 58:24.915
(Cornell) Get a chance to catch any beads?

58:25.044 --> 58:26.500
(Laughter continues)

58:34.887 --> 58:36.843
(Cornell) How about them doubloons?

58:36.972 --> 58:38.963
(Laughter continues)
